### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَٱلَّذِينَ يُمَسِّكُونَ بِٱلْكِتَـٰبِ وَأَقَامُوا۟ ٱلصَّلَوٰةَ إِنَّا لَا نُضِيعُ أَجْرَ ٱلْمُصْلِحِينَ</span>

### English

As for those who firmly abide by the Scripture and establish prayer—surely We never discount the reward of those acting righteously.